---
layout: default
---
<div class="post">
  <article>
    <!-- Hero section: centered photo + name + subtitle -->
    <div class="about-hero" style="text-align: center; padding: 0.8rem 0 0.5rem;">
      {% if page.profile %}
        {% if page.profile.image %}
          {% assign profile_image_path = page.profile.image | prepend: 'assets/img/' %}
          {% if page.profile.image_circular %}
            {% assign profile_image_class = 'img-fluid z-depth-1 rounded-circle' %}
          {% else %}
            {% assign profile_image_class = 'img-fluid z-depth-1 rounded' %}
          {% endif %}
          <div class="profile-photo-wrap" style="width: 210px; height: 210px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 50%; ">
            {%
              include figure.liquid loading="eager" path=profile_image_path class=profile_image_class sizes="180px" alt=page.profile.image
              cache_bust=true
            %}
            <style>
              .about-hero .profile-photo-wrap figure,
              .about-hero .profile-photo-wrap picture {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
              }
              .about-hero .profile-photo-wrap img {
                width: 100% !important;
                height: 100% !important;
                object-fit: cover !important;
                object-position: center 55% !important;
              }
            </style>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endif %}

      <h1 class="post-title" style="margin-bottom: 0.2rem; font-size: 2.5rem;">
        {% if site.title == 'blank' %}
          <span class="font-weight-bold">{{ site.first_name }}</span> {{ site.middle_name }}
          {{ site.last_name }}
        {% else %}
          {{ site.title }}
        {% endif %}
      </h1>
      <p class="desc" style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">{{ page.subtitle }}</p>

      <!-- Social icons right under name -->
      {% if page.social %}
        <div class="social" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
          <div class="contact-icons">{% include social.liquid %}</div>
          <div class="contact-note">{{ site.contact_note }}</div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <!-- Bio -->
    <div class="about-bio" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      {{ content }}
    </div>

    <!-- News -->
    {% if page.news and site.announcements.enabled %}
      <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
          <a href="{{ '/news/' | relative_url }}" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">News</a>
        </h2>
        {% include news.liquid limit=true %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Latest posts -->
    {% if site.latest_posts.enabled %}
      <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2>
          <a href="{{ '/blog/' | relative_url }}" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">latest posts</a>
        </h2>
        {% include latest_posts.liquid %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Selected papers -->
    {% if page.selected_papers %}
      <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 3.5rem;">
          <a href="{{ '/publications/' | relative_url }}" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">Selected Publications</a>
        </h2>
        {% include selected_papers.liquid %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Teaching & Outreach -->
    <div class="about-bio" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 3.5rem auto 0;">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Teaching &amp; Outreach</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.8rem;">Outside of research, I really enjoy teaching and mentorship! Over the past few years, I've been lucky to have the chance to work with students across a range of courses and settings.</p>

      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem;">

        <div>
          <strong>CMS 144: Networks: Structure &amp; Economics</strong><br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Teaching Assistant, Caltech &middot; Winter 2025</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>CS 38: Algorithms</strong><br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Teaching Assistant, Caltech &middot; Spring 2023, Spring 2024</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>CS 21: Decidability &amp; Tractability</strong><br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Teaching Assistant, Caltech &middot; Winter 2023</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>ACM 104: Applied Linear Algebra</strong><br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Teaching Assistant, Caltech &middot; Fall 2023</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Ph 1a: Newtonian Mechanics</strong><br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Grader, Caltech &middot; Fall 2022</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong><a href="https://www.aspirations.org/aic-campus-reps" target="_blank">NCWIT</a></strong> &mdash; National Center for Women &amp; Information Technology<br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Campus Representative, Caltech &middot; Outreach &amp; mentorship for women in CS.</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong><a href="https://www.algostem.org/" target="_blank">AlgoSTEM</a></strong> &mdash; STEM education nonprofit<br>
          <span style="color: var(--global-text-color-light); font-size: 0.95rem;">Co-Founder &middot; 100k+ enrollments across free STEM courses and camps.</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    {% if site.newsletter.enabled %}
      {% include scripts/newsletter.liquid center=true %}
    {% endif %}
  </article>
</div>
